    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="dev-tools"><a href="#dev-tools" class="headerlink" title="dev tools"></a>dev tools</h2><ul><li><a href="https://jsonformatter.com/">JSON formatter live &#x2F; minimalist json formatter</a> </li><li><a href="https://crontab.guru/">Crontab.guru - The cron schedule expression editor</a></li><li><a href="https://mongoplayground.net/">Mongo Playground</a></li><li><a href="https://nginx-playground.wizardzines.com/">Nginx Playground</a></li><li><a href="https://codingspeedtest.com/">Coding Speed Test</a> - 打字速度测试, 可以自选编程语言</li><li><a href="https://regexlearn.com/zh-cn/learn">Regex - Playground</a></li><li><a href="https://cmdchallenge.com/">cmd 有趣在线挑战</a></li></ul><h2 id="dev-cheatsheets"><a href="#dev-cheatsheets" class="headerlink" title="dev cheatsheets"></a>dev cheatsheets</h2><ul><li><a href="https://roadmap.sh/roadmaps">Developer Roadmaps</a> - 学习不同工具或技术的分步指南和路径</li><li><a href="https://devhints.io/">Devhints Cheatsheets</a> - 开发提示备忘录</li></ul><h2 id="network"><a href="#network" class="headerlink" title="network"></a>network</h2><ul><li><a href="https://iknowwhatyoudownload.com/en/peer/">I Know what your download</a> - 我知道你下载了什么, 追踪 ip 的 bt 下载列表</li><li><a href="https://www.zerotier.com/">ZeroTier</a> - 跨网段打隧道组建虚拟子网, 比如打通公司与家庭网络, 从公司访问家里的 Nas</li><li><a href="https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdGuardHome">AdGuardHome</a> - DNS 服务器, 防劫持 &amp; 广告过滤</li></ul><h2 id="resources"><a href="#resources" class="headerlink" title="resources"></a>resources</h2><ul><li><a href="https://annas-archive.org/">安娜的档案</a> - 电子书下载, 免登录</li></ul><h2 id="笔记"><a href="#笔记" class="headerlink" title="笔记"></a>笔记</h2><ul><li><a href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a> - 个人知识库, <a href="https://zettelkasten.de/introduction/zh/">卢曼卡片盒笔记法介绍</a></li></ul><h2 id="白噪音"><a href="#白噪音" class="headerlink" title="白噪音"></a>白噪音</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.lofi.cafe/">lofi.cafe - lofi music 🎧</a></li></ul><h2 id="人格测试"><a href="#人格测试" class="headerlink" title="人格测试"></a>人格测试</h2><ul><li><a href="https://www.16personalities.com/ch">16Personalities</a> - 16型人格测试</li></ul><h2 id="chrome-extension"><a href="#chrome-extension" class="headerlink" title="chrome extension"></a>chrome extension</h2><ul><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/immersive-translate-web-p/bpoadfkcbjbfhfodiogcnhhhpibjhbnh">沉浸式翻译</a></li><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/wikiwand-wikipedia-modern/emffkefkbkpkgpdeeooapgaicgmcbolj">Wikiwand: Wikipedia Modernized</a></li><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/adblock-%E2%80%94-best-ad-blocker/gighmmpiobklfepjocnamgkkbiglidom">AdBlack</a></li><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/enhanced-github/anlikcnbgdeidpacdbdljnabclhahhmd/related">Enhanced GitHub</a> - Github 增强, 下载单文件</li><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/proxy-switchyomega/padekgcemlokbadohgkifijomclgjgif">Proxy SwitchyOmega</a> - 浏览器代理切换</li><li><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/singlefile/mpiodijhokgodhhofbcjdecpffjipkle">SingleFile</a> - 把文件保存到一个文件中</li></ul><h2 id="mac-platform"><a href="#mac-platform" class="headerlink" title="mac platform"></a>mac platform</h2><ul><li><a href="https://bobtranslate.com/">Bob</a> - 划词翻译、截图翻译与截图 OCR</li><li><a href="https://magnet.crowdcafe.com/">Magnet</a> - 任务窗口管理</li><li><a href="https://caffeinated.app/">Caffeinated</a> - 让 Mac 保持唤醒状态</li></ul><h2 id="others"><a href="#others" class="headerlink" title="others"></a>others</h2><ul><li><a href="https://tinypng.com/">TinyPNG – Compress PNG images while preserving transparency</a> - 在线图片压缩, 也提供 API</li><li><a href="https://smsreceivefree.com/">Receive SMS Online | Temporary SMS and Disposable Numbers</a> - 免费的国外接码平台</li><li><a href="https://damngood.tools/tools/idea-filter">Idea filter</a> - 列出想法以及限制条件, 看想法是否具备可行性</li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
